{"type": "article", "id": 21469, "title": "墙面书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-29T07:33:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 115, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021355087u1XMhpAzYZ2qLBc.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一组可以灵活改变形状的架子，它的模块是两个垂直相交的板。特别在于他们不是以中心点交叉，而是留有短边和长边。多个架子可以变化不同的方向拼起来，变成一个大的格子式的架子。中间的格子是正方形或长方形，而架子的四周是开放的，与墙面更融合，简单灵活而带有装饰性。它有白色和黑色两种，<a href=\"http://www.benthansen.net/en/products/up-the-wall/assemble-shelves\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509514blBgNWfIu29iQ6s.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509513JuFcnZTOEvVMGys.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150951IK69c2e5Onwuftx0.jpg\" width=\"595\" height=\"367\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61680672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150952sPr351QexGHVNJDy.jpg\" width=\"597\" height=\"377\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63149079\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}